sb: Controls the Strawbees Robotic Inventions for the micro:bit board[Cannot find this string]
sb.getHexColorFromHSB:
Hexadecimale weergave van een kleur op basis van de `tint`,
`verzadiging` and `helderheid` van een kleur.
sb.getHexColorFromHSB|param|hue: Tint van een kleur van `0` tot `100`
sb.getHexColorFromHSB|param|saturation: Verzadiging van een kleur van `0` tot `100`
sb.getHexColorFromRGB:
Hexadecimale weergave van een kleur op basis van de hoeveelheid
`rood`, `groen` and `blauw` van een kleur.
sb.getHexColorFromRGB|param|blue: Hoeveelheid blauw in een kleur van `0%` tot `100%`
sb.getHexColorFromRGB|param|green: Hoeveelheid groen in een kleur van `0%` tot `100%`
sb.getHexColorFromRGB|param|red: Hoeveelheid rood in een kleur van `0%` tot `100%`
sb.setContinuousServoSpeed:
Stel de snelheid in van een 360° servo van `-100%` tot
`100%`. Werkt alleen goed als een 360° is aangesloten.
sb.setContinuousServoSpeed|param|servo: Which continuous servo to set the speed to.
sb.setNeoPixelColor: Sets the color of an individual NeoPixel by specifying the color by name.
sb.setNeoPixelColorHSB:
Sets the color of an individual NeoPixel by specifying the amount of
hue, saturation and brightness in the color. The amounts range from
`0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorHSB|param|brightness: Brightness of the color, ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorHSB|param|hue: Hue of the color, ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorHSB|param|neoPixel: Which NeoPixel to set the color.
sb.setNeoPixelColorHSB|param|saturation: Saturation of the color, ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorRGB:
Sets the color of an individual NeoPixel by specifying the amount of
red, green and blue in the color. The amounts range from `0%` to
`100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorRGB|param|blue: Amount of blue in color ranging, from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorRGB|param|green: Amount of green in color ranging, from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColorRGB|param|neoPixel: Which NeoPixel to set the color.
sb.setNeoPixelColorRGB|param|red: Amount of red in color ranging, from `0%` to `100%`.
sb.setNeoPixelColor|param|color: The name of the color from a list of color labels.
sb.setNeoPixelColor|param|neoPixel: Which neoPixel to set the color.
sb.setServoPosition:
Sets the position of a servo by specifying a value ranging from `0%` to
`100%`.
sb.setServoPosition|param|servo: Which servo to set the position to.
sb.transitionServoPosition:
Transtions the position of a servo over a duration of time (in seconds).
The "shape" of the transition is specified by choosing one of the easing
functions by name.
sb.transitionServoPosition|param|duratio: The duration of the transition, in seconds.
sb.transitionServoPosition|param|servo: Which servo to set the position to.
sb.turnOffServo:
Turns a servo off so that no force will be applied and it can be rotated
manually. This saves battery.
sb.wave:
Samples the vale of a periodic wave function. The wave starts at the
beginning of the running time. It can be configured by specifying it's
length (in seconds), amplitude and offset.
sb.waveTypeLabel: A label of a wave type.
sb.wave|param|length: The length (or period) of the wave, in seconds.
